1
00:00:00,508 --> 00:00:08,608
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

2
00:00:08,783 --> 00:00:17,020
<i>Even if you get lost, let's start walking</i>

3
00:00:17,258 --> 00:00:19,249
<i>One more time</i>

4
00:00:22,263 --> 00:00:26,029
<i>Are you really happy</i>

5
00:00:26,100 --> 00:00:29,467
<i>when you're always meeting</i>
<i>to someone's expectations?</i>

6
00:00:29,670 --> 00:00:33,231
<i>Even if you change to</i>
<i>who you really wanna be</i>

7
00:00:33,608 --> 00:00:36,975
<i>Will you always have a great smile?</i>

8
00:00:37,044 --> 00:00:44,473
<i>Dreaming of only "the beginning,"</i>
<i>I wake up</i>

9
00:00:44,552 --> 00:00:53,688
<i>and someday, I'll live on my own.</i>

10
00:00:53,761 --> 00:01:01,793
<i>Yes, precious things are never in shape</i>

11
00:01:02,036 --> 00:01:08,874
<i>You never know what it is</i>
<i>when you get it or lose it</i>

12
00:01:08,943 --> 00:01:17,009
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

13
00:01:17,318 --> 00:01:25,783
<i>Even if you get lost,</i>
<i>let's start walking</i>

14
00:01:25,860 --> 00:01:27,885
<i>One more time</i>

15
00:01:31,777 --> 00:01:32,436
Sakura!

16
00:01:33,879 --> 00:01:36,507
It was worth teaching you Genjutsu
in survival training

17
00:01:36,582 --> 00:01:38,277
during the Genin Exam.

18
00:01:39,284 --> 00:01:41,878
You truly have a talent for it.

19
00:01:42,554 --> 00:01:43,077
Huh?

20
00:01:44,256 --> 00:01:47,020
Release the Genjutsu and
wake up Naruto and Shikamaru!

21
00:01:48,227 --> 00:01:50,092
Naruto will be delighted.

22
00:01:51,396 --> 00:01:52,556
He'll be getting a mission
after such a long while.

23
00:01:54,266 --> 00:01:55,255
What do you mean by a mission?

24
00:01:56,168 --> 00:01:57,499
Be careful...

25
00:01:59,104 --> 00:02:02,301
It's the first A Ranked mission
since the Land of the Waves.

26
00:02:02,374 --> 00:02:09,280
<i>Village in Distress.</i>
<i>A New A Ranked Mission!</i>

27
00:02:13,318 --> 00:02:16,776
Sensei! What do you mean by A Ranked
mission in the condition we are in?!

28
00:02:16,855 --> 00:02:18,413
What do we have to do?!

29
00:02:19,424 --> 00:02:21,858
Sasuke is chasing Gaara and company
of the Sand Village.

30
00:02:23,629 --> 00:02:24,220
Sakura...

31
00:02:25,097 --> 00:02:27,691
Release the Genjutsu
on Naruto and Shikamaru,

32
00:02:28,200 --> 00:02:29,531
and go after Sasuke.

33
00:02:33,939 --> 00:02:36,999
<i>I feel uneasy...</i>
<i>about that unusual Chakra.</i>

34
00:02:46,184 --> 00:02:47,549
But then,

35
00:02:47,619 --> 00:02:49,849
we should wake up Ino and Choji
and go in a large group.

36
00:02:50,489 --> 00:02:53,185
There may already
be quite a large number

37
00:02:53,258 --> 00:02:55,818
of Sand and Sound Shinobi
who have infiltrated this village.

38
00:02:58,063 --> 00:03:02,159
Actions lose quickness when there's more
than the fundamental four in a squad...

39
00:03:02,234 --> 00:03:04,759
and it becomes difficult to
hide from the enemy.

40
00:03:06,705 --> 00:03:09,902
You learned that in the Academy's
patrol practical training, right?

41
00:03:11,076 --> 00:03:15,809
Oh, I see! Then four means
that you'll come with us...

42
00:03:15,881 --> 00:03:18,577
No, I must not leave here.

43
00:03:19,451 --> 00:03:20,281
Summoning Jutsu!

44
00:03:26,825 --> 00:03:30,761
As for the rest, this Pakkun will
track down Sasuke by scent!

45
00:03:32,130 --> 00:03:35,190
C-Could it be...
the one other member is this puppy?!

46
00:03:38,270 --> 00:03:43,333
Hey! Little girl!
Don't you be calling me a cute puppy!

47
00:03:44,509 --> 00:03:46,909
<i>I didn't say...cute.</i>

48
00:03:47,713 --> 00:03:51,205
Okay, Sakura! Release the Genjutsu
on Naruto and Shikamaru!

49
00:03:51,950 --> 00:03:52,507
Okay!

50
00:04:08,367 --> 00:04:09,061
<i>Release!</i>

51
00:04:17,876 --> 00:04:19,571
What is it... Sakura?

52
00:04:20,879 --> 00:04:21,470
Get down!

53
00:04:23,148 --> 00:04:25,309
I'll tell you later!
Just stay down!

54
00:04:33,325 --> 00:04:36,624
Shikamaru... you were...
from the beginning...

55
00:04:41,566 --> 00:04:43,329
Owwee!

56
00:04:43,668 --> 00:04:46,034
You were able to release Genjutsu, too!

57
00:04:46,304 --> 00:04:48,272
Why were you pretending
to be asleep?!

58
00:04:48,607 --> 00:04:51,405
Humph! I don't want to
end up getting involved!

59
00:04:51,710 --> 00:04:55,009
Heck no...
I could care less about Sasuke!

60
00:04:58,650 --> 00:05:00,117
Owwee!

61
00:05:17,035 --> 00:05:19,367
W-What's going on...?

62
00:05:19,704 --> 00:05:20,671
Naruto! Behind you!

63
00:05:25,410 --> 00:05:26,707
F-Fast...

64
00:05:26,878 --> 00:05:28,402
Not just fast...

65
00:05:33,051 --> 00:05:33,949
Guy Sensei!

66
00:05:36,655 --> 00:05:38,247
Now, I'll announce the mission!

67
00:05:38,790 --> 00:05:40,587
As soon as you've heard what
the mission is, go through that hole.

68
00:05:42,093 --> 00:05:44,891
Track down Sasuke,
join up and then stop him!

69
00:05:45,263 --> 00:05:47,959
Then await next orders
in a safe place.

70
00:05:48,667 --> 00:05:50,931
Huh? Did something happen
to Sasuke?!

71
00:05:51,603 --> 00:05:52,968
I'll tell you the reason en route!

72
00:05:54,072 --> 00:05:54,766
Let's go

73
00:05:56,708 --> 00:05:58,767
Jeez... Why me?

74
00:05:59,144 --> 00:06:00,270
Hey, boy!

75
00:06:00,645 --> 00:06:01,304
Huh?

76
00:06:01,546 --> 00:06:03,446
If this mission is a success,

77
00:06:03,682 --> 00:06:06,742
as a reward I'll let you
touch my paw-pads.

78
00:06:06,952 --> 00:06:08,544
So don't sulk like that!

79
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:09,482
Huh?

80
00:06:09,688 --> 00:06:10,780
See?

81
00:06:11,556 --> 00:06:13,046
They're soft and supple!

82
00:06:13,325 --> 00:06:14,952
Su... pple...?

83
00:06:15,460 --> 00:06:16,791
Yes, very...

84
00:06:18,463 --> 00:06:21,330
Soft and Supple!

85
00:06:25,604 --> 00:06:26,798
Let's just go!

86
00:06:28,974 --> 00:06:30,032
H-Hey!

87
00:06:33,612 --> 00:06:35,307
Will it be okay with just them?

88
00:06:36,047 --> 00:06:39,107
They'll be okay.
Pakkun is with them.

89
00:06:40,352 --> 00:06:42,411
As long as they don't pursue too far...

90
00:07:01,540 --> 00:07:04,509
To think I'd be able to fight you again...

91
00:07:08,980 --> 00:07:12,177
This barrier can't be broken
unless it's from the inside.

92
00:07:13,518 --> 00:07:17,079
If Lord Hokage would just
take out one of those four,

93
00:07:17,155 --> 00:07:18,486
we could help...

94
00:07:19,524 --> 00:07:22,220
Hey, it's gonna start soon.

95
00:07:22,794 --> 00:07:24,955
Put up a barrier on the inside, too!

96
00:07:25,564 --> 00:07:26,258
Sure!

97
00:07:41,112 --> 00:07:45,014
Hm... It doesn't look like
I'll be able to get out this easily.

98
00:07:46,051 --> 00:07:48,042
You don't really mean that.

99
00:07:48,119 --> 00:07:53,421
It'd be tougher for you if someone
came in and got in the way, right?

100
00:08:09,774 --> 00:08:11,674
Ninja Art: Tile Shuriken!

101
00:08:14,479 --> 00:08:15,776
That's too easy!

102
00:08:16,815 --> 00:08:18,077
Striking Shadow Snake!

103
00:08:23,121 --> 00:08:25,214
With such a weak technique...

104
00:08:25,724 --> 00:08:29,660
It sucks to get old, eh,
Sarutobi Sensei?

105
00:08:37,669 --> 00:08:38,499
<i>Substitution?!</i>

106
00:08:45,310 --> 00:08:47,141
Earth Style: Great Mud River!

107
00:08:51,716 --> 00:08:53,081
Is this it?

108
00:08:53,251 --> 00:08:54,616
I don't think so!

109
00:08:55,620 --> 00:08:57,110
Earth Style: Earth Dragon Bomb!

110
00:09:01,059 --> 00:09:02,287
Fire Dragon Bomb!

111
00:09:08,533 --> 00:09:10,398
He's combined Earth and Fire!

112
00:09:11,002 --> 00:09:12,401
Excellent, Lord Hokage!

113
00:09:20,979 --> 00:09:24,142
Stop the stupid act, Orochimaru.

114
00:09:27,619 --> 00:09:29,450
Very good...

115
00:09:31,990 --> 00:09:35,016
Really, I've been grossly underestimated.

116
00:09:35,727 --> 00:09:40,096
Did you think you could kill me
with that level of Jutsu?

117
00:09:40,665 --> 00:09:44,829
Humph... A hateful fellow as usual!

118
00:09:45,203 --> 00:09:47,103
Don't say that.

119
00:09:47,872 --> 00:09:53,333
A high maintenance student is cute.
Right, Sarutobi Sensei?

120
00:10:07,826 --> 00:10:09,350
<i>Something's strange...</i>

121
00:10:10,161 --> 00:10:13,130
<i>All of the Academy's classes</i>
<i>doing self study.</i>

122
00:10:14,532 --> 00:10:15,760
<i>And that smoke...</i>

123
00:10:17,135 --> 00:10:18,864
<i>That's coming from the direction</i>
<i>of the exam arena.</i>

124
00:10:21,439 --> 00:10:23,873
<i>Isn't there some disturbance</i>
<i>to the east?</i>

125
00:10:24,709 --> 00:10:26,802
<i>I wonder if something happened...</i>

126
00:10:28,279 --> 00:10:29,871
<i>This is definitely strange!</i>

127
00:10:37,388 --> 00:10:41,290
But sudden self study is
sure a smack in the eye!

128
00:10:41,459 --> 00:10:43,427
It's been like this for a while!

129
00:10:43,495 --> 00:10:47,022
Yeah. Iruka Sensei
and everyone are late...

130
00:10:47,432 --> 00:10:49,195
Aren't they, Konohamaru?

131
00:10:57,142 --> 00:10:58,700
Konohamaru?

132
00:10:59,310 --> 00:11:00,334
Yikes!

133
00:11:01,212 --> 00:11:03,510
Jeez, what is this?!

134
00:11:04,415 --> 00:11:07,612
And Mom just bought this for me!

135
00:11:08,353 --> 00:11:11,447
I'll loan you my colored pencil.

136
00:11:11,589 --> 00:11:16,686
What're you saying?!
This color is this spring's new color!

137
00:11:16,761 --> 00:11:19,321
Aww, what'll I do?

138
00:11:30,942 --> 00:11:31,840
<i>That is...?</i>

139
00:11:36,347 --> 00:11:40,249
I wonder if Naruto and the others
went to stop Sasuke?

140
00:11:40,752 --> 00:11:41,980
Those brats?

141
00:11:42,487 --> 00:11:46,583
But surely, some Genin won't
be able to make any difference...

142
00:11:50,028 --> 00:11:53,395
Hm? Is this the data of
that kid back there?

143
00:11:55,333 --> 00:11:57,130
You give him too much credit.

144
00:11:58,169 --> 00:11:59,067
Think again!

145
00:12:00,338 --> 00:12:02,898
You'll trip up if you underestimate him.

146
00:12:29,968 --> 00:12:31,094
Teachers Office

147
00:12:31,169 --> 00:12:34,866
There is information that several units
have already infiltrated the village...!

148
00:12:36,040 --> 00:12:40,033
We should evacuate the students
to a safe place right away!

149
00:12:40,311 --> 00:12:44,680
Yes... And without causing panic
among the students!

150
00:12:45,283 --> 00:12:47,717
Then let's evacuate the students

151
00:12:47,785 --> 00:12:49,844
as soon as possible under
the pretense of an evacuation drill!

152
00:12:59,864 --> 00:13:02,890
Isn't it about time
we stopped playing around?

153
00:13:03,368 --> 00:13:05,893
This isn't an Academy class, so...

154
00:13:07,639 --> 00:13:09,402
You have a point.

155
00:13:13,111 --> 00:13:15,477
Did you foresee your final moments?

156
00:13:55,353 --> 00:13:58,754
I won't go easy on you
just because you're doddering.

157
00:14:00,425 --> 00:14:02,052
I look forward to it.

158
00:14:02,593 --> 00:14:04,424
Depending on your Jutsu,

159
00:14:04,495 --> 00:14:08,056
I might have to have you
start over at the Academy!

160
00:14:10,268 --> 00:14:12,930
Please don't disappoint me too much!

161
00:14:26,684 --> 00:14:27,810
W-Wow...

162
00:14:28,386 --> 00:14:29,819
What Chakra?!

163
00:14:30,388 --> 00:14:33,949
Yeah... It seems the air is
bearing down within the body!

164
00:14:40,465 --> 00:14:42,592
<i>Shuriken Shadow Clone Jutsu!</i>

165
00:14:48,439 --> 00:14:50,669
<i>Summoning Jutsu. Reanimation!</i>

166
00:14:51,809 --> 00:14:52,969
<i>That technique!</i>

167
00:14:53,511 --> 00:14:54,102
One!

168
00:14:55,747 --> 00:14:57,806
He is using a Summoning Jutsu
as a shield.

169
00:14:58,516 --> 00:15:00,074
And this dead person is...

170
00:15:00,218 --> 00:15:01,150
Two!

171
00:15:03,488 --> 00:15:05,513
I must stop the third one at any cost...!

172
00:15:05,957 --> 00:15:06,821
Three!

173
00:15:18,703 --> 00:15:23,106
<i>It looks like the third one was no good.</i>
<i>Oh well...</i>

174
00:15:27,445 --> 00:15:29,845
<i>It looks like I stopped the third one.</i>

175
00:15:30,348 --> 00:15:33,078
<i>Now, this is where it gets tough...</i>

176
00:15:34,652 --> 00:15:38,179
<i>He summoned those two of all people...</i>

177
00:15:54,305 --> 00:15:56,671
I-It can't be!
Those personages are...!

178
00:15:57,508 --> 00:15:58,998
Those personages are?

179
00:15:59,710 --> 00:16:04,147
Now, what will you do,
Sarutobi Sensei...?

180
00:16:04,782 --> 00:16:05,578
No...

181
00:16:13,391 --> 00:16:16,588
Lord... Third Hokage

182
00:16:20,164 --> 00:16:23,258
Okay! Everyone, please move quickly!

183
00:16:27,705 --> 00:16:29,900
Oh, what a day!

184
00:16:30,174 --> 00:16:34,304
My favorite colored pencil
didn't have to break like that!

185
00:16:35,146 --> 00:16:39,845
Lousy evacuation drill...
Self study was better.

186
00:16:40,151 --> 00:16:44,087
Konohamaru's been quiet, hasn't he?
I wonder what's wrong?

187
00:16:44,155 --> 00:16:45,918
Huh? Yeah.

188
00:16:46,524 --> 00:16:49,084
<i>After the whole school does</i>
<i>a long self study,</i>

189
00:16:49,393 --> 00:16:51,953
<i>the whole school does</i>
<i>an evacuation drill.</i>

190
00:16:52,396 --> 00:16:54,057
<i>This is too strange!</i>

191
00:16:55,366 --> 00:16:57,630
Okay! Stop! Get in line!

192
00:16:58,736 --> 00:17:00,431
<i>That look on Iruka Sensei's face...</i>

193
00:17:00,938 --> 00:17:02,803
<i>Something's definitely going on here!</i>

194
00:17:04,775 --> 00:17:05,503
<i>And also...</i>

195
00:17:10,214 --> 00:17:13,581
Okay, everyone!
Don't go off on your own.

196
00:17:22,059 --> 00:17:26,223
<i>That rainbow... It's been</i>
<i>bugging me for a while!</i>

197
00:17:33,070 --> 00:17:36,665
What's that, Old Man?
There's a strange rainbow!

198
00:17:42,914 --> 00:17:45,109
It's an unusual rainbow!

199
00:17:46,117 --> 00:17:48,347
Do you like rainbows, Konohamaru?

200
00:17:48,853 --> 00:17:53,483
Yeah! And I've never seen
such a pretty rainbow!

201
00:17:54,358 --> 00:17:58,124
I see, I see.
But, Konohamaru...

202
00:17:58,462 --> 00:17:59,258
Hmm?

203
00:18:00,765 --> 00:18:04,826
Rainbows used to symbolize snakes...

204
00:18:05,403 --> 00:18:09,100
And it's said that they bode evil.

205
00:18:09,674 --> 00:18:14,008
Such a pretty thing? That's a lie!

206
00:18:14,745 --> 00:18:16,042
I see, I see.

207
00:18:23,287 --> 00:18:26,916
<i>Symbolizes snakes...</i>
<i>Is something happening?</i>

208
00:18:42,373 --> 00:18:44,933
Long time no see... Saru.

209
00:18:45,243 --> 00:18:49,373
Oh, it's you...
You've gotten old, Sarutobi.

210
00:18:50,081 --> 00:18:55,519
I never thought I would meet
the great brothers in this manner...

211
00:18:56,887 --> 00:18:58,149
It's regretful.

212
00:18:58,789 --> 00:18:59,847
This is bad.

213
00:19:00,391 --> 00:19:01,824
That Summoning Jutsu...

214
00:19:02,627 --> 00:19:04,595
Who in the world are they?!

215
00:19:05,563 --> 00:19:07,326
Please prepare yourselves...

216
00:19:07,832 --> 00:19:08,890
Lord First Hokage...

217
00:19:09,634 --> 00:19:10,896
Lord Second Hokage!

218
00:19:13,371 --> 00:19:14,235
That's right...

219
00:19:14,839 --> 00:19:16,636
The one with the black hair
is the First Hokage.

220
00:19:17,141 --> 00:19:19,006
The one with the white hair
is the Second Hokage.

221
00:19:20,711 --> 00:19:22,872
They are both reputed to
be the highest Shinobi

222
00:19:22,947 --> 00:19:25,882
and they are the Hokages
who built the today's Leaf Village!

223
00:19:31,889 --> 00:19:33,379
Reanimation, huh?

224
00:19:34,225 --> 00:19:37,023
This youth summoned us with
the Forbidden Jutsu, then?

225
00:19:37,595 --> 00:19:38,960
He's something else...

226
00:19:40,931 --> 00:19:42,865
Then, Sarutobi!

227
00:19:43,401 --> 00:19:48,031
Does this mean we must... fight you?

228
00:19:48,506 --> 00:19:51,339
Let's stop the old people
get together talk...

229
00:19:51,709 --> 00:19:53,370
Shall we get started?

230
00:19:54,111 --> 00:19:56,909
There's always fighting...
no matter when you live.

231
00:19:58,716 --> 00:20:00,047
You like that, don't you?

232
00:20:00,551 --> 00:20:05,989
No good will come by deriding the dead
and playing around with time!

233
00:20:13,898 --> 00:20:16,696
I get it! So that's what happened!

234
00:20:21,172 --> 00:20:23,504
That Sasuke, getting all impatient!

235
00:20:23,574 --> 00:20:27,635
So, why am I pulled into this?!
This is such a drag!

236
00:20:27,912 --> 00:20:31,279
It can't be helped!
It's Kakashi Sensei's order.

237
00:20:34,185 --> 00:20:34,981
This way!

238
00:20:52,236 --> 00:20:53,498
That brat, huh...

239
00:20:54,872 --> 00:20:55,600
Let's go

240
00:21:05,916 --> 00:21:15,985
<i>Everyone makes mistakes</i>
<i>It's nothing to be ashamed about</i>

241
00:21:16,427 --> 00:21:27,270
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>
<i>Walk with a smile</i>

242
00:21:37,381 --> 00:21:43,013
<i>Yes, breathe in the air</i>
<i>Lift your face to the sky and jump</i>

243
00:21:43,087 --> 00:21:48,047
<i>If it rains, take a break</i>
<i>Go where the wind takes you</i>

244
00:21:48,426 --> 00:21:53,329
<i>So many regrets</i>
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>

245
00:21:53,397 --> 00:21:58,528
<i>Let's go carve the badges in our chest</i>
<i>Yes, it's Show Time, life begins now.</i>

246
00:21:58,602 --> 00:22:08,773
<i>Everyone makes mistakes</i>
<i>It's nothing to be ashamed about</i>

247
00:22:09,079 --> 00:22:19,512
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>
<i>Walk with a smile</i>

248
00:22:19,590 --> 00:22:30,159
<i>Transform sadness into the wind</i>
<i>and continue to forge on</i>

249
00:22:30,234 --> 00:22:35,797
<i>Forge on strong</i>

250
00:22:47,719 --> 00:22:50,711
Darn it! The pursuer is too fast!

251
00:22:50,789 --> 00:22:54,088
Once we Genin get caught,
that will be the end.

252
00:22:54,326 --> 00:22:56,556
In that case,
we should ambush and attack them.

253
00:22:56,628 --> 00:22:58,755
I already thought of it,
but it'll probably be no use.

254
00:22:58,830 --> 00:23:00,991
Then, what should we do?!

255
00:23:01,066 --> 00:23:05,435
There is only one choice.

256
00:23:06,004 --> 00:23:09,838
Next time, "A Shirker's Call to Action:
Layabout No More!"

257
00:23:09,908 --> 00:23:12,035
It isn't my style,
but we have no choice, I guess.
